combat:
 - terrain
 - - Terrain Cost
 - - Terrain Height
 - - A* path-finding
 - Character Customization
 - - Skills
 - - - Base Skills (Str, Int, Dex, End, Spd, Agl)
 - - - - Thought: Available action points are determined by Agl.
             Each action point left at EoT grants a dodge roll during combat.
 - - - Weapon Skills (based on weapon type)
 - - Equipment 
 - - - Weapons
 - - - - Varied types (sword, spear, bow for starters, can expand later)
 - - - - Each weapon will have associated Base Skills.
 - - - - Weapon Skill determines hit chance
 - - - - Associated base skills modify damage
 - - - Armour
 - - - - Armour Rating gives flat damage reduction
 - - - - Heavy Armours have higher DR but have negative impact on Spd and Agl


